Considering I can do 12k damage to 24k mobs in Valor grouped and never get agro even with a Warrior MT, I think I know what I am talking about.<br>
While in a group that has another 65 wiz that waits until 50% to cast sunstrike and then we play chase the wizard while he's trying to chain cast concussion to get the mob off him.<br>
<br>
Notice also, I've got SCS2.<br>
<br>
Concussion most certainly is NOT neccessary.  Just some folks got so used to using a crutch they can't imagine doing anything without it.<br>
<br>
Knowing what to cast when is &gt; concussion. <p>Aazumar Dracostarr<br>
